settings.description: A remixed version of those hand trap stages from SMB3 world 8, just a bit harder..
An old test level developed in July of 2021, mainly created to test how Bowser statues react to certain properties. Rel: 1/21/2023, 12:10pm ... #8992-062, also, Happy New Year!
Mario goes through the starting area of Bowser's Airship and must defeat boom boom. Bowsers airship 2 is next.
